Package: ggbrandon
Title: Brandon-Style Themes and Utilities for ggplot2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Brandon", "Lukas", email = "blukas4@uic.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Brandon-style ggplot2 themes and helper functions for 
    generating clean, publication-ready plots. Includes custom axis styling, 
    uniform text and line sizing, and dimension reduction plot themes. Designed 
    for consistent, reproducible plotting workflows, especially in single-cell 
    and genomics applications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    legendry
